{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1714900807.837021", "card_id": "Q_655002697", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 252}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "持有逾 1800 亿美元现金却不投资，巴菲特表示，只在正确的时候挥杆一击，你觉得什么是正确的时候？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 4 日，在巴菲特 2024 年股东大会上，伯克希尔哈撒韦董事长沃伦·巴菲特解释了为何他并不急于动用公司逾 1800 亿美元的庞大现金储备。巴菲特表示，不会在 5.4% 这么高利率的情况下使用这笔钱，只在正确的时候挥杆一击。为何持有逾 1800 亿美元现金不投资？巴菲特：只在正确的时候挥杆一击丨一手"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a61ee6a29e7f9fb25a3b1afd295a0770_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "555 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/655002697"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIppmI4NuNwfoFEAMaCTEwNzgzMzg3OCDH9NqxBjAAOKYFQAByCTY1NTAwMjY5N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1714900807.837927", "card_id": "Q_654985250", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 87}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价雷军对张朝阳说:「科普高中物理就行了，不要科普大学物理、博士物理，我听不懂啊」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "雷军对物理书喊跪 张朝阳回应：太谦虚 有空切磋"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-81ffce0ebc732132c27c9fab3046f4c7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "367 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/654985250"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIppmI4NuNwfoFEAMaCTEwNzgyOTkyOSCZxtmxBjAAONoBQAFyCTY1NDk4NTI1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "2_1714900807.838854", "card_id": "Q_654481002", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531c